<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .invitation-details {
        background-color: #e3f2fd;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .accept-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #28a745;
        color: white;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 10px 5px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .decline-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #6c757d;
        color: white;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 10px 5px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        padding-top: 20px;
        border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #666;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>🏠 Joyful Journey Family Invitation</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h2>You're invited to join <%= @family.name %>!</h2>
      
      <p>Hi there!</p>
      
      <p><strong><%= @inviter.name %></strong> has invited you to join their family on Joyful Journey, where families share and preserve their most precious memories together.</p>
      
      <% if @invitation.message.present? %>
        <div class="invitation-details">
          <h3>Personal Message:</h3>
          <p><em>"<%= simple_format(@invitation.message) %>"</em></p>
        </div>
      <% end %>
      
      <div class="invitation-details">
        <h3>What is Joyful Journey?</h3>
        <p>Joyful Journey is a private family platform where you can:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>📸 Share photos and memories</li>
          <li>🎉 Track family milestones</li>
          <li>👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 Connect with family members</li>
          <li>📝 Create posts about special moments</li>
          <li>🗓️ Follow family timelines</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <p>This invitation will expire on <strong><%= @invitation.expires_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %></strong>.</p>
      
      <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <a href="<%= @invitation_url %>" class="accept-button">Accept Invitation</a>
      </div>
      
      <p>If you don't want to join this family, you can simply ignore this email.</p>
      
      <p>If you have any questions, please contact <%= @inviter.name %> directly.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This invitation was sent to <%= @invitation.email %> by <%= @inviter.name %> from <%= @family.name %>.</p>
      <p>If you received this email by mistake, please ignore it.</p>
      <p>You can also visit the link above to decline the invitation if you prefer.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>